    <h1 itemprop="headline" class=" ">Donald Trump criticised by veterans for wearing military style outfit despite &#039;dodging&#039; Vietnam draft</h1>

    
            <div class="intro">
                <p>President is not first to have donned military garb but is first to have insulted a Gold Star family</p>
      </div>
            <ul class="caption meta inline-pipes-list">
              <li class="author" itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
          <span itemprop="name"><a href="/author/will-worley" title="Will Worley" itemprop="sameAs">Will Worley</a></span>
                  </li>
                    <li>
          <a href="https://twitter.com/willrworley">@willrworley</a>
        </li>
                    <li title="4 March 2017 16:23 London"><time data-microtimes='{"published":"1488548700000","display":0,"changed":"1488644598000"}' datetime="Sat, 03/04/2017 - 16:23" unixtime="1488644598000">Saturday 4 March 2017 16:23 GMT</time></li>
                    <li class="comments">
          <a href="#commentsDiv" id="comment-count" class="icon-comment"></a>
